{"tid":2261526,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"囚犯賄運違禁品 兩懲教被捕","createTime":"2020-10-28T11:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:15:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63f7b4c7600e6f16e2f649ca3cd3886fdf91974d","tid":2261526,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/FV7YAJQBUFAE3ADTEBKQ5KS4UY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FFV7YAJQBUFAE3ADTEBKQ5KS4UY%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7PLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=f895ed9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FFV7YAJQBUFAE3ADTEBKQ5KS4UY%2F&h=4fb1b9ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/FV7YAJQBUFAE3ADTEBKQ5KS4UY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n囚犯賄運違禁品 兩懲教被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yQMwT_bITO-ypvKkIHTVivYd90U=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQFQGZSKXBCL5PLJM5VK6DMQ7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyQMwT_bITO-ypvKkIHTVivYd90U%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQFQGZSKXBCL5PLJM5VK6DMQ7M.jpg&h=d1362b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■塘福懲教所兩名職員涉收取賄款後，將違禁品帶入監獄。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾爆出多宗囚犯管理問題的塘福懲教所，再爆出有懲教助理疑受賄為囚犯提供違禁品被捕。據悉，有人收取六位數賄款，將違禁品帶入監獄交給囚犯，兩名懲教助理被捕，昨已正式停職候查。消息稱，廉政公署及懲教署人員上周五，突擊搜查塘福懲教所的工場及監倉，起獲手機、香煙及內藏色情影片的USB。兩署均拒評事件。<br />\n<br />\n來自前線懲教人員的消息指，被捕兩人。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可疑手機訊號揭發<br />\n<br />\n據了解，二人涉收取高達六位數字賄款後，將違禁品非法帶給囚犯，事件中約10名囚犯被處分，需暫時單獨監禁或調往其他監獄，避免「夾口供」，部份涉事囚犯有黑幫背景。傳聞指，有囚犯欲取得手機娛樂甚至聯絡外界，並欲獲額外香煙在獄中出售圖利或賭博，遂行賄懲教署人員，以求對方協助把違禁品運入懲教所。<br />\n<br />\n據知，懲教署發現獄中有可疑手機訊號，遂與廉署聯手調查，兩署上周五行動中，在塘。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署發言人指，不評論個別個案，強調注重所有人員的品德、誠信及操守。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f9bffc2c7d912766eaf1a5b1eda0f9b4efbd4afe","tid":2261526,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"懲狗同黑狗根本同源黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec05c86cdd644c9142279f0ae23f22187b3df6e","tid":2261526,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"傾唔掂或者得罪上頭啫,扮有紀律嘅無紀律部隊"}]}